data.description: Step into the warm embrace of your dream sanctuary on Holts Landing Road! This delightful 4-bedroom, 2-bath single-family ranch home is a cozy haven designed for comfort and style. Recently adorned with a fresh coat of paint and new, inviting flooring in the kitchen, family room, and 4th bedroom, this residence radiates a homely ambiance.  As you cross the threshold, you'll uncover a lovingly crafted floor plan, seamlessly merging practicality with a touch of classic charm. The kitchen, undoubtedly the heart of the home, invites connection and conversation. With its new flooring, and fresh paint. You have ample counter space and functional layout with space for counter stools and dining table, it promises a delightful cooking experience. The adjacent family room and living room provide generous spaces for family and friends to gather, creating memories that will last a lifetime.  Escape to the privacy of the fenced-in backyard, where you can unwind and entertain with ease. Whether you're hosting a barbecue or simply enjoying a quiet evening under the stars beside the fire pit, this outdoor space is a true retreat.  Situated near state parks and a convenient boat launch, outdoor enthusiasts will find plenty to explore just moments from home. And with Bethany Beach just a short drive away, you can easily indulge in the sun, sand, and surf whenever the mood strikes.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this meticulously maintained ranch home yours. Schedule a showing today and envision the lifestyle that awaits you!
